{
  "stem": "2620.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Then, then we-- it came-- it came-- orders came that we were going to have to leave from here, too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they boxed us in the cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And there was another camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Muhldorf was not in the Waldlager, it was not in the forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was another camp also, in the same village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they boxed us both from both camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And boxed us in and we kept on going and going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were going to take us to the Taurus, around the Taurus Mountains, but the train couldn't go through anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were going to take us to liquidate us, to kill us over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what they did-- You knew that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we heard that afterwards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, we didn't know that at first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found that out later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one time they, they'd gone back and forth, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The train kept on going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It seemed like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then one time, the train stops in a-- in a-- in a village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, everybody out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the transport fuhrer who was in charge of the transport said, the war is over, and you are all free to go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know what to do, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So better go here, to go there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody went, you know, in different directions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was this the Americans that said, you're free?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still the Germans who said it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the transport fuhrer, the one who was in charge of the transport, said, you're all free to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that wasn't really true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were surrounded and they were shooting at us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of people-- a lot of people got killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
